_:N5454c57dba964d13a4afa74ec6caadbe <http://schema.org/name> "Esme Winch" .
_:N5454c57dba964d13a4afa74ec6caadbe <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Esme Winch joined the Further Education (FE) Commissioner team in 2019 as an FE Adviser. She was appointed Deputy FE Commissioner in January 2026.</p>\n\n<p>She has held a number of roles in the FE sector including:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Group Finance and Resources Director, NCG</li>\n  <li>Managing Director and Chief Financial Officer, NCFE</li>\n  <li>Chief Executive and Principal, Loughborough College</li>\n</ul>\n" .
